	<internal-name>Intro</internal-name>
	<sectionClass_s>no-margin-top</sectionClass_s>
	<file-name>99c73f96-40e9-3d2e-93ad-00eac944613a.xml</file-name>
	<sectionContent_html>&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;I have a question for you:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;What do the following three things have in common?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol style="color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Realising that you&amp;rsquo;re out of milk just as you sit down to eat your cereal.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;The devastation of getting dumped by your first love in high school.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Becoming disabled, or dying, without having insurance in place.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;If you answered, &amp;lsquo;they&amp;rsquo;re all things we didn&amp;rsquo;t plan for&amp;rsquo; then you&amp;rsquo;d be right. Although to be fair, if you&amp;rsquo;d answered &amp;lsquo;they all suck&amp;rsquo; then I&amp;rsquo;ll admit you were right about that one too.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Death and disability insurance is one of those things that we hate thinking about and so it becomes something that many of us don&amp;rsquo;t correctly plan for, or don&amp;rsquo;t plan for at all. This is especially problematic if you&amp;rsquo;re married or in a long-term relationship.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Time to change that.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Today, we&amp;rsquo;re talking about life and disability insurance planning for young couples. If you love your partner and want to ensure that both of you are taken care of if the worst happens, as I&amp;rsquo;m sure you do, then this is one that we all need to pay attention to.&lt;/p&gt;</sectionContent_html>
