	<bg_color_s>bg--yellow</bg_color_s>
	<call_out_content_html>&lt;h2 class="title--md no-margin-top" style="margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: var(--heading-line-height); font-weight: 500; font-size: 32px; margin-top: 0px; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-style: italic; background-color: #ffbe00; color: #323232 !important;"&gt;With that in mind, we&amp;rsquo;re going to look at the three things you need to know about disability and life insurance planning for yourself and your partner.&lt;/h2&gt;</call_out_content_html>
