	<file-name>5da11811-a7d7-bc11-ebff-7ac6c732ec6a.xml</file-name>
	<call_out_content_html>&lt;h2 class="title--md no-margin-top" style="color: var(--color-text-heading); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: var(--heading-line-height); font-weight: 500; font-size: 32px; margin-top: 0px; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-style: italic; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;For all of these reasons, step one in this process is to discuss the issue of disability and death and its financial consequences with your partner and make sure that you both clearly understand one another&amp;rsquo;s contributions to the &amp;lsquo;household&amp;rsquo; expenses, and what sort of insurance each of you will need to cover the contribution each of you makes.&lt;/h2&gt;</call_out_content_html>
