	</item>	<item datasource="sections" inline="true">	<key>3eb7e8b2-461d-a835-09c8-6215163899a1</key>
	<value>Sec 2</value>
<component id="3eb7e8b2-461d-a835-09c8-6215163899a1">
	<content-type>/component/component-articlesection</content-type>
	<display-template>/templates/web/components/article-section.ftl</display-template>
	<no-template-required/>
	<merge-strategy>inherit-levels</merge-strategy>
	<objectGroupId>3eb7</objectGroupId>
	<objectId>3eb7e8b2-461d-a835-09c8-6215163899a1</objectId>
	<file-name>3eb7e8b2-461d-a835-09c8-6215163899a1.xml</file-name>
	<internal-name>Sec 2</internal-name>
	<sectionClass_s>no-margin-bottom</sectionClass_s>
	<sectionContent_html>&lt;h2 class="text--md" style="color: var(--color-text-heading); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); line-height: var(--heading-line-height); font-weight: 500; font-size: var(--text-md); font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;2. Understand the options available to you&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Ideally, each of you should consider taking out both an income protection policy, and a life insurance policy. Those are the minimums to ensure that neither you nor your partner is financially crippled if the other is disabled, falls seriously ill, or dies.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;For a more comprehensive approach to insuring your finances, you may want to consider additionally taking out critical illness cover. These are policies that will cover the related expenses that you will incur following a disability or serious illness. For example, that might include things like medical bills, or shortfalls in medical-aid payouts, or even the cost of lifestyle adjustments.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h2 class="text--md" style="color: var(--color-text-heading); margin-bottom: var(--space-sm); line-height: var(--heading-line-height); font-weight: 500; font-size: var(--text-md); font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;3. Implement an insurance plan to suit your lifestyle&lt;/h2&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;As a younger couple, you probably have fewer assets with more expenses and loads of future expenses. For example, you are likely to buy a bigger house when you decide to start a family, or you might decide to spend your money funding more expensive cars or starting a business.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Whatever the case may be, you need to choose insurance options that are affordable enough so that you can sustain those premium payments throughout the various phases of life through which you will still travel.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;For that reason, you should look at structuring your insurance plan in a way that suits your lifestyle and makes it as affordable as possible to continue paying your premiums. Basically, your insurance needs to be implemented with a long-term view so that it serves all your needs for the entire time you need it, while being affordable throughout your changing life circumstances and phases.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;And finally, a note about marriage.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;If you&amp;rsquo;re still planning to get married, you need to understand that in South Africa there are three different marital regimes, or &amp;lsquo;types&amp;rsquo; of marriage and your marriage regime will impact your finances and your insurance. They are:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ol style="color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Marriage in community of property&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Marriage out of community of property (without accrual)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Marriage out of community of property (with accrual)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ol&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;If you just go ahead and get married without signing any marriage contract beforehand, your marriage will be constituted legally under South Africa&amp;rsquo;s default marriage type: a marriage in community of property. This means that, in simple terms, both of you own an equal share of everything in the marriage. And by &amp;lsquo;everything&amp;rsquo;, we mean everything: even debt that your spouse had before you got married. You now share 50/50 in the commitment of repaying the debt.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p style="margin-bottom: var(--space-md); line-height: var(--body-line-height); color: #2e2e31; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-size: 14px; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Alternatively, you can choose to be married out of community of property. This will require that both you and your partner enter into an antenuptial contract prior to saying your vows. The details of this marriage regime and the two variations are beyond the scope of this blog, but I&amp;rsquo;ve included it here because the type of marriage regime your union is classified under, will have an impact on your life insurance.&lt;/p&gt;</sectionContent_html>
