	<objectId>8c09f89c-bbc2-e732-0762-fc0ac4f5ba87</objectId>
	<file-name>8c09f89c-bbc2-e732-0762-fc0ac4f5ba87.xml</file-name>
	<internal-name>Callout right one</internal-name>
	<call_out_content_html>&lt;h2 class="title--md no-margin-top" style="color: var(--color-text-heading); margin-bottom: 0px; line-height: var(--heading-line-height); font-weight: 500; font-size: 32px; margin-top: 0px; font-family: 'Whitney SSm A', 'Whitney SSm B', system-ui, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif, 'Apple Color Emoji', 'Segoe UI Emoji', 'Segoe UI Symbol'; font-style: italic; background-color: #f9f9f9;"&gt;Regardless of the type of marriage regime that your union is recognised under, for the sake of your insurance, it's vital that both of you get assistance with drafting a last Will and testament. This document will detail how each of your assets and liabilities will be dealt with upon your death as well as detail your estate planning in general; and how estate duty should be resolved.&lt;/h2&gt;</call_out_content_html>
